    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 96.</p><p>Tier III: Overlord</p><p>Prerequisite: Thrall, Soul Harvest</p><p>Enfeebling Terror. Creatures that are frightened by you are also Impaired for the duration.</p><p>Apotheosis. Once per long rest, as an action, you undergo a terrifying transformation, channeling the full depth of your dark power. For 1 minute, you gain the following benefits:</p><p>Your spells and class features ignore immunity to the frightened condition for the duration. +</p><p>When you cast a spell that deals damage, it deals maximum damage instead of rolling. +</p><ul><li></li></ul><p>When a creature dies within 120 feet of you, you can choose to automatically raise it as a thrall without requiring a reaction, ignoring your normal thrall limit for the duration. Thralls raised in this manner crumble to dust when your Apotheosis ends.</p><p>Path Connections Sovereign. Instead of the Thrall Heroic Perk, you can take the Greater Charms Perk, changing to the Sovereign path.</p></div>",
